description:
Help From On High

The Reverend Tingley knew his days were numbered... he had built the mission in the hills of Northern China thirty years before... survived the endless small wars fought by the warlords... the Japanese invasion... but, not, the enemy was on the doorstep again... this time the Chinese people's Army... the Communists! And they were a greater menace than any who had come before!

Smitty Chickens Out

The G.I.s in the squad looked up to the veteran Sergeant who had more medals than a room full of Generals! Bernie Smith scolded his inexperienced men. Protected them in battle, and kept most of them alive in the inter of 1951 somewhere around the 38th parallel in that corner of the world called Korea...

Little War

They had orders not to fight... but the Red Chinese were pouring over the border... their buddies were dying in the tall grass... and the three American military advisors could either join the battle or see the men they'd trained be wiped out! So they started their own... Little War

description:
Corporal in Command

Cpl. Carl Brady had just been commissioned in the field for one simple reason! Every Officer from Captain Klein on down was dead or back in the field hospital... all the Sergeants had had it... and it was up to Bray to get the pitifully few men left up onto the ridge! This was February, 1945... Von Rundstedt's Nazis were fighting fanatically to hold their position... and the regiment would be wiped out if Lt. Bray's company failed! The Nazis' heavy M.G.S. were the key... and Brady knew there was only one way they could be silenced!

Eager For Defeat

The American patrol moving into the Hedgerow were far in advance of their fellows... and the Nazis opened a hole for them to enter their lines, then closed it behind them! A Nazi tank clanked out of the brush ...the G.I.s seemed confused... frightened... their weapons dropped... their hands went upward... they somehow seemed... Eager For Defeat

Always Alert (Text Only Story)

The Colonel's Reunion

Retired U.S. Army Colonel Samuel G. Lufton was in his middle fifties when he accepted employment running an oil pumping station somewhere in the African interior! The Communists, always eager to fill a political vacuum, had wrested control from the legitimate government! A Chinese militarist, Li Yeng, headed the Reds' motley Army... to a man, they were merciless thieves who took special delight in harassing Americans like the Colonel!

description:
"To Be a R.E.B.E.L.," part 2! As the R.E.B.E.L.S. openly challenge the Green Lantern Corps for the hearts and minds of the galaxy, Starfire learns the horrifying truth about the Psions – the alien race that destroyed her people.

Altin Ad'Ms and Gorius are infront of the Guardians of the Universe explaining what went wrong in their sector. Why Vril Dox is seemingly crontrolling the sector, why there is so much unrest and more importantly why did Gorius kill hundreds of her own spieces.

Gorius tries to defends her actions by explaining that she saw Starfire and know that she to had been torqured by the Psions. She begs Starfire to fallow her to her home planet of Psion and shows Starfire the atrocities that go on there. Starfire is moved by what the Green Lantern shows her and helps to stop the male Psions from using the females as test subjects and breeders. Just when i looks like the two heros might be helping, the male Psions blow up the female's testing lab destroying all evidence and killing hundreds.

Meanwhile, back at Rebel command, Adam Strange is tryin to convince the rest of the team that Vril is acting crazy and needs to be removed from power. Vril proves he is still incontrol by taking various actions. Most of all dropping that Psion contract because of what Starfire found, and because of what Starfire threaten to do.
name: To Be A R.E.B.E.L., Part 2

description: THE RETURN OF WANDA MAXIMOFF! The search for the Scarlet Witch is finally over as the Young Avengers find Wanda. But is she a hero or a villain? Is she still the Scarlet Witch? The battle over Wanda rages on as Avengers go up against the Young Avengers, Magneto clashes with Quicksilver, Wonder Man battles Wolverine, and the most powerful villain in the Marvel Universe conspires against them all so that he can possess Wanda himself.

No More Notches!

The two men facing him were strangers... but their flashing sixguns where aimed at him, they were in railhead to get him! Billy the Kid had no time to think while his colt bucked ...but when it was over, there remained no time! And he vowed there'd be... No More Notches!

Chained Gun Lightning

Clayton Rall and his daughter, Laura, were going West to stay! Rall had thirty thousand in cash with him he intended to invest where he settled... but he had no intention of making his home in the midst of violence where gun-fighting was prevalent! Billy the Kid learned that quickly... ...and tried his best to change!

Concerning the Cowboy (Text only story)

The Next Victim

Pistol Passport

The early days of the settlement of Wyoming were raw and dangerous! To this new land came the pioneers, men and women looking for a fresh start... here too, came the outlaws and toughs, banding together to prey on honest folks! The largest and worst of these outlaw groups was Frog Yates' hole-in-the wall gang, and to them came a stranger carrying his passport to lawlessness on his hip...

The Kid Rides Again

My name is Ken Ford! I'm a writer of the Western scene! The story of Billy the Kid had always fascinated me and now I've come to the place where he had lived and fought to get the color, the rawness of that fabulous era, to write the true story of Billy the Kid!
